    <detaileddescription>
<para>Storage abstraction for the SQL catalog.</para>
<para><computeroutput>CatalogStore</computeroutput> persists SQL catalog rows. <computeroutput>SqlCatalog</computeroutput> owns Iceberg catalog semantics and uses this interface for database-specific row operations. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
